## Website Structure

- Releases
	- Release JBC001
	- Release JBC002
- Artists
	- Artist 001
	- Artist 002
- Mixes
	- Mix 001
	- Mix 002
- About
- Privacy Policy 
- Contact
- Home

#### Release

- Release No
- Title
- Artist
- Description
- Image
- Soundcloud Url
- Buy link - Bandcamp or Beatport
- Mp3 upload / download

#### Artist

- Name
- Image
- Biography
- Soundcloud
- Facebook
- Twitter

#### Mix

- Mix no
- Title
- Description
- Image
- Artist
- Soundcloud Url